The fault occurs in OslcQueryResult::getNextPageUrl()

The selector misses the nextPage statement.

A possible solution could be to change these lines in the getNextPageUrl method:

Selector select = new SimpleSelector(infoResource, predicate, (RDFNode) null);
StmtIterator iter = rdfModel.listStatements(select);
if (iter.hasNext()) {
    Statement nextPage = iter.next();
    nextPageUrl = nextPage.getResource().getURI();
}   else {
    nextPageUrl = "";
}

to --------

ResIterator iterator = rdfModel.listSubjectsWithProperty(predicate);
nextPageUrl = "";

if (iterator.hasNext()) {
    Resource aResource = iterator.next();
    Statement nextPage = aResource.getProperty(predicate);
    if (nextPage!=null) {
	nextPageUrl = nextPage.getResource().getURI();
    }
}

