ServiceProvider serviceProvider = client.getResource(serverProviderURL,OslcMediaType.APPLICATION_RDF_XML).getEntity(ServiceProvider.class);

but instead before when using Service and PrefixDefinition, example
Service service = client.getResource(serverProviderURL,OslcMediaType.APPLICATION_RDF_XML).getEntity(Service.class);

